Warsaw,YouTube,"How can you not mention the Royal Łazienki Park, one of the most beautiful places in Warsaw, and Wilanów Palace? There are more places to eat and meet, like Koszyki, the Powiśle Power Plant, and Norblin. I also recommend the University of Warsaw library and the park on its roof. There's also an interesting Warsaw Uprising Museum.","how can you not mention the royal łazienki park, one of the most beautiful places in warsaw, and wilanów palace? there are more places to eat and meet, like koszyki, the powiśle power plant, and norblin. i also recommend the university of warsaw library and the park on its roof. there's also an interesting warsaw uprising museum.",Nötr
Warsaw,YouTube,"Oh Jesus. This is no Warsaw. This is some vanilla version for foreigners to show off. I wish you could see Warsaw like it use to be in 60s or 70s. Grey, dirty, stinky,super depressing. Streets are full with "" pijaczkis"". On the corners ""wystajrogi"". Gangs of "" Git ludzi, prawilnych bez kicioru"". I'm front of few hotels toothless prostitutes. Near the railroad stations "" pedaly"". THIS was the WARSAW. it have energy and character. Uniqueness and heart. Not this foo foo postcards. Do you want to see WARSAW???? Go to BRZESKA street. Take a raid to East side of Vistula River. That's where really Warsaw is hiding. That's where soul of this City is","oh jesus. this is no warsaw. this is some vanilla version for foreigners to show off. i wish you could see warsaw like it use to be in 60s or 70s. grey, dirty, stinky,super depressing. streets are full with "" pijaczkis"". on the corners ""wystajrogi"". gangs of "" git ludzi, prawilnych bez kicioru"". i'm front of few hotels toothless prostitutes. near the railroad stations "" pedaly"". this was the warsaw. it have energy and character. uniqueness and heart. not this foo foo postcards. do you want to see warsaw???? go to brzeska street. take a raid to east side of vistula river. that's where really warsaw is hiding. that's where soul of this city is",Nötr
