Warsaw,YouTube,"Like this video... it says all. Facts. Homelessness and drug use in 90s oh goshe. Main station was like one vast toilet. And people injecting kompot, Polish homemade heroine. In warsaw it was normal to see. That time in poland peeps were drunkards and in shops were selling cheap meat and white bread. Shops were diffrently filled... different things people were buying. And its funny cause its only 25 years diffrence and the vibe is very diffrent.","like this video... it says all. facts. homelessness and drug use in 90s oh goshe. main station was like one vast toilet. and people injecting kompot, polish homemade heroine. in warsaw it was normal to see. that time in poland peeps were drunkards and in shops were selling cheap meat and white bread. shops were diffrently filled... different things people were buying. and its funny cause its only 25 years diffrence and the vibe is very diffrent.",Nötr
Warsaw,YouTube,"I dont know... its another modernised city, in global world. Which stands for multicultural peoples origin. Thing is, it has character which is a little bit diffrent. Cause there is only one capital of poland 🇵🇱 with polish language etc. Doesnt know full picture of reality of warsaw. Been there and seem lovely fresh young people which contradicts to what seeing normally in Scotland nowadays. At day or night the place seemed very calmed down people very well beheved. Out of world experience to what I knew before. Means poland in past, or todays Scotland. Seemed they were/are deprived places. So having a trip to city which is mostly modernised, where population is young and looking forward to progress... at the same time safe and peaceful. Its is joyous experience. Remember warsaw of 90s 30 years ago, it had very diffrent character. Today's one is much more pleasant, but that past was much more normal for poland familiar. There was lot of fights hools crimes drugs a looot. Today's there is no sign for it anymore. By the spirit energy it seems like a diffrent place. Easiness is today. Womans looks feminine. Hahah. Surprise. Hahahha. it could be said it a bit unreal. Even by the food in zabka you can guess its diffrent world. Hahaha. Shelf look neat clean and products are healthy options. And this is fact for whole warsaw in general and no wonder you paid twice as much money for living than in krakow. Seriously better energy in warsaw. You may not like prices lack of historical sites or many other aspects. But as energy, spirit quality warsaw is top in poland as for my taste. And top of most of western Europe places, where only occasionally there are quality findings.","i dont know... its another modernised city, in global world. which stands for multicultural peoples origin. thing is, it has character which is a little bit diffrent. cause there is only one capital of poland 🇵🇱 with polish language etc. doesnt know full picture of reality of warsaw. been there and seem lovely fresh young people which contradicts to what seeing normally in scotland nowadays. at day or night the place seemed very calmed down people very well beheved. out of world experience to what i knew before. means poland in past, or todays scotland. seemed they were/are deprived places. so having a trip to city which is mostly modernised, where population is young and looking forward to progress... at the same time safe and peaceful. its is joyous experience. remember warsaw of 90s 30 years ago, it had very diffrent character. today's one is much more pleasant, but that past was much more normal for poland familiar. there was lot of fights hools crimes drugs a looot. today's there is no sign for it anymore. by the spirit energy it seems like a diffrent place. easiness is today. womans looks feminine. hahah. surprise. hahahha. it could be said it a bit unreal. even by the food in zabka you can guess its diffrent world. hahaha. shelf look neat clean and products are healthy options. and this is fact for whole warsaw in general and no wonder you paid twice as much money for living than in krakow. seriously better energy in warsaw. you may not like prices lack of historical sites or many other aspects. but as energy, spirit quality warsaw is top in poland as for my taste. and top of most of western europe places, where only occasionally there are quality findings.",Nötr
