Warsaw,YouTube,"If you ever plan to explore more of Warsaw — there’s so much beyond the Old Town and the main tourist spots! Definitely check out Centrum Praskie Koneser and the new Bohema complex (it’s shaping up to be great), Nocny Market on Towarowa 3 for amazing vibes and street food, Bulwary Wiślane for summer evenings of course!, and Park Skaryszewski for a green escape. And don’t miss the charming Francuska street in Saska Kępa! And oh... I can go on and on. :D And if you want to practice Polish... here’s a tip: find people who are used to helping foreigners. We Poles can speak really slowly and clearly when we know someone’s learning (sometimes like a friendly bear reading bedtime stories ). A few of my own 'bears' have made it to B2 level already — so you’ll be in great company. :D :D Oh one more small tip: did you know there’s such a thing as a Warsaw noise map? I always check it when looking for a new place to live — very helpful to know if you’re moving into a quiet spot or somewhere with a lot of city buzz.","if you ever plan to explore more of warsaw — there’s so much beyond the old town and the main tourist spots! definitely check out centrum praskie koneser and the new bohema complex (it’s shaping up to be great), nocny market on towarowa 3 for amazing vibes and street food, bulwary wiślane for summer evenings of course!, and park skaryszewski for a green escape. and don’t miss the charming francuska street in saska kępa! and oh... i can go on and on. :d and if you want to practice polish... here’s a tip: find people who are used to helping foreigners. we poles can speak really slowly and clearly when we know someone’s learning (sometimes like a friendly bear reading bedtime stories ). a few of my own 'bears' have made it to b2 level already — so you’ll be in great company. :d :d oh one more small tip: did you know there’s such a thing as a warsaw noise map? i always check it when looking for a new place to live — very helpful to know if you’re moving into a quiet spot or somewhere with a lot of city buzz.",Nötr
Warsaw,YouTube,"I can recommend you restaurant Mei kuchnia koreańska. I have been to Warsaw twice in recent years and I miss this food very much. It's a shame that Warsaw is so far away because I could go there just to eat the chicken again Unfortunately, I don't remember what the dish was called, but the other dishes were good too. After the last concert in Warsaw that I attended, I fell in love with this city, but I live in the countryside near Krakow and I wouldn't trade it for any big city. anyway I wish you all the best, I watch your channel and I am full of admiration that you like Poland. maybe 20 years ago I would have thought you were crazy, but seeing how Poland has changed for the better in recent years, and the rest of the world has gone crazy... I am not surprised that you like it here. me too! I am glad that I was born in this country.","i can recommend you restaurant mei kuchnia koreańska. i have been to warsaw twice in recent years and i miss this food very much. it's a shame that warsaw is so far away because i could go there just to eat the chicken again unfortunately, i don't remember what the dish was called, but the other dishes were good too. after the last concert in warsaw that i attended, i fell in love with this city, but i live in the countryside near krakow and i wouldn't trade it for any big city. anyway i wish you all the best, i watch your channel and i am full of admiration that you like poland. maybe 20 years ago i would have thought you were crazy, but seeing how poland has changed for the better in recent years, and the rest of the world has gone crazy... i am not surprised that you like it here. me too! i am glad that i was born in this country.",Nötr
